title: ‘The Summer I Turned Pretty’ Brand Collabs Keep Coming Post-Season 3 Finale
summary: The Sept 17. finale doesn't mean the limited-edition, show-inspired partnerships are through. After all, there's still a movie in the works.

title: XG Can Turn Any Stage Into the Met Gala
summary: The seven-piece global group, back with their fashion-forward new single “Gala,” have made style a large part of their artistic identity: “It’s more than just dressing up. It's a creative way to learn and express who we are.”

title: Business travel and expense startup Navan files for initial public offering in booming deal market
summary: Business travel and expense startup Navan has filed for an initial public offering, reporting an annual revenue rate surpassing $600 million.
